exercises.text:
Review the definitions of the following concepts:

(a) trapdoor one-way function;

(b) RSA equations;

(c) prime number theorem;

(d) square-and-multiply algorithm;

(e) H\u00e5stad's attack;

(f) Miller's theorem;

(g) discrete logarithm problem;

(h) generator of $\mathbb{Z}_p^*$;

(i) Diffie\u2013Hellman key exchange.
